ActAgreement Between the Inuit of the Nunavut Settlement Area and Her Majesty the Queen in right of Canada
SubjectOrder Authorizing the Transfer of Administration and Control of Lands in Arctic Bay and Clyde River, Nunavut
PrecisOrder (1) authorizing the RELINQUISHMENT by the COMMISSIONER OF NUNAVUT of the administration and control of parcels of land in ARCTIC BAY and CLYDE RIVER, Nunavut; and (2) authorizing the TRANSFER of the administration and control of those lands to the GOVERNMENT OF CANADA.
